snippet.title: Oop! 😂
snippet.description:
The decades-long debate over censorship and a woman’s body reached a new height after Madonna slammed Instagram for removing a photo of her exposed nipple. Is this another case of a woman’s body being overly sexualized or was Madge in the wrong? Plus, Amber Rose’s ex campaigns for forgiveness on Instagram, but is that enough? Watch the full conversation here: https://youtu.be/rflCFyz8kyI
